text: Aerenea subimpetiginosa is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1948. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Aerenea subimpetiginosa. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Compsosomatini Category:Beetles described in 1948
